<p>The following breakpoints are used by this theme and are automatically generated from toweltheme.breakpoints.yml:</p>
<ul>
  <li>
    <p>Breakpoint Mobile</p>
    <ul>
      <li>
        <p><em>*The mobile breakpoint has no media query</em></p>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Breakpoint Narrow ($breakpoint-narrow)</p>
    <ul>
      <li>
        <p>all and (min-width: 480px)</p>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Breakpoint Normal ($breakpoint-normal)</p>
    <ul>
      <li>
        <p>all and (min-width: 768px)</p>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Breakpoint Wide ($breakpoint-wide)</p>
    <ul>
      <li>
        <p>all and (min-width: 1280)</p>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ul>
<p> They can be used in scss like so:</p>
<pre>
.example-class {
  @include susy-media($breakpoint-narrow) {
    background-color: #ff5400;
  }
}
</pre>
<p>Other breakpoints may eventually be defined directly in scss/components/_breakpoints.scss if they do not need to be accessed from PHP or JS.</p>
